              "name": "GM Core",
              "page": 334,
              "type": "source"
            }
          ],
          "text": "Time creatures are natives of the Dimension of Time. They don\u2019t age, and while some might be driven by supernatural hungers, they don\u2019t need to eat or drink to survive. They can survive the basic environmental effects of the Dimension of Time.",
