          "name": "Vulnerable to Curved Space",
          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "When a hound of Tindalos is not adjacent to a structural angle of 90\u00b0 (or more acute), its resistance to physical damage is suppressed and it becomes sickened 1. It can't recover from this sickened condition, but the condition ends automatically once the hound is again adjacent to a suitable angle.",
          "type": "stat_block_section"
        }
